title: Ross Marquand on Die Hard
itunes:title: Ross Marquand on Die Hard
description:
This week Chuck had the pleasure of sitting down with The Walking Dead's Ross Marquand to talk celebrity impressions, life, art and one of, if not the best action movies of all time, DIE HARD. Giggles abound.
